ttps://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AF%D8%A7%D9%81%D9%8E%D8%B9%D9%8E"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to defend"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to ward off, keep off"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to hinder, delay, put off"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"motivator, stimulus, driver","examples":[{"text":"البحث والتطوير هو إحدى دوافع عجلة النمو الإقتصادي","english":"research and development is one of the drivers of economic development (“the wheel of economic growth”)"}]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Derived from the active participle of دَفَعَ (dafaʕa, “to push”)."},"ipa":["/daː.fa.ʕa/","/daː.fiʕ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n12726","headword_ar":"دَافِعٌ","root":"dfE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[act. part. n. of 1]. It is said in the Kur [lii. 8],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA lahu mino daAfiEK","text_ar":"مَا لَهُ مِنْ دَافِعٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There shall not be any repeller thereof."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd.) And in the same [lxx. 2],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"layosa lahu daAfiEN","text_ar":"لَيْسَ لَهُ دَافِعٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There shall not be for it any repeller:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any defender."},{"kind":"text","text":"(B.) ―         -b2-  Applied to a ewe or she-goat, (S,) or to a she-camel, (S, K,) as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daAfiEapN","text_ar":"دَافِعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"midofaAEN","text_ar":"مِدْفَاعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"That infuses"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tadofaEu","text_ar":"تَدْفَعُ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the first milk into her udder"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"secretes it therein"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a little before bringing forth;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that infuses the milk into her udder when about to produce her young, by reason of its abundance:"},{"kind":"text","text":"AO says that some make"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mufokihN","text_ar":"مُفْكِهٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daAfiEN","text_ar":"دَافِعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"to signify the same, [i. e., to signify as explained above, or nearly so,] saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"hiYa daAfiEN biwaladK","text_ar":"هِىَ دَافِعٌ بِوَلَدٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and if you will, you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"hiYa daAfiEN","text_ar":"هِىَ دَافِعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", alone. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["Bd","S","K"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}